                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8352" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2095</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1239 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">转紫海，向新生——安吉大竹园村的民宿集群转型发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Turn to the purple sea, run to the new —— Anji Dazhuyuan village B&amp;B cluster transformation and development road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐清，马晨昕，陈婧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安吉县灵峰街道大竹园村村民委员会</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">基层部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">紫海战略；民宿集群；转型发展；大竹园村</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Purple Sea Strategy; B&amp;B Cluster; Transformation and Development; Dazhuyuan Village</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">我国民宿行业正处于增量竞争阶段，在新时代消费升级驱动下，民宿行业发展应顺应市场环境和客户需求的变化。本案例主要回顾了大竹园村由单一的乡村民宿集群发展，迭代转型为“民宿集群+”产业延伸的战略抉择过程。在“民宿集群”发展初期阶段，大竹园村受到产品单一、同质化竞争等发展困境；基于返乡青年的创业回归契机，以及周边内外部市场的深度调研后，通过紫海战略决策，寻找民宿市场的红海与蓝海特征，招引咖啡休闲、田园研学、露营基地等多元业态；通过“民宿集群+”产业链延伸，让村庄的“家门口”经济成功转型发展，实现共同富裕与高质量发展。本案例旨在启发学生对紫海战略的内涵及内外部环境评估能力的理解，系统思考紫海战略实施过程的驱动因素、核心能力及商业模式的创新与控制。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">China&#39;s B&amp;B industry is in the stage of incremental competition. Driven by the new era of consumer upgrading, the development of the B&amp;B industry should be in line with the changes in the market environment and customer demand. This case mainly reviews the strategic choice process of Dazhuyuan Village from the development of a single rural B&amp;B cluster to the iterative transformation into a &quot;B&amp;B cluster +&quot; industry extension. In the early stage of the development of &quot;B&amp;B cluster&quot;, Dazhuyuan Village suffered from the development difficulties of single product and homogenized competition; based on the entrepreneurial return opportunity of returning youths, as well as the in-depth research of the surrounding internal and external markets, Dazhuyuan Village has adopted the purple sea strategic decision to look for the characteristics of the red sea and blue sea of the B&amp;B market, and to attract the diversified industries such as coffee recreation, garden study and camping bases, etc.; through the &quot;B&amp;B cluster+&quot; strategic choice process, Dazhuyuan Village has developed into a rural B&amp;B cluster. Through the extension of the industry chain of &quot;B&amp;B cluster +&quot;, the village&#39;s &quot;home&quot; economy has successfully transformed and developed, realizing common prosperity and high-quality development. This case aims to inspire students to understand the connotation of purple sea strategy and the ability to assess the internal and external environments, and to think systematically about the driving factors, core competencies, business model innovation and control in the implementation process of purple sea strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">紫海战略的企业内外部环境；紫海战略内涵与差异化策略；核心能力理论及战略转型的内外部驱动因素；商业模式创新与控制的认识与运用</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
